{ I think that 16...f5!, as Carlsen played, is very idea-based and good. But, 16..Be6 is also simple enough and good enough - let us say both are good moves. I made Carlsen's game informational, so you don't train both moves, you can consider them to be alternatively good. Hope, that helps! }
